snippet.textDisplay: Covid-19 is in Briarcliff Nursing Home in my small town of Carthage, TX (2 cases reported as of 2 days ago. My aunt is in there. I kept trying to tell people to stop being so hateful and more informative than shaming. People were saying things like “Louisiana, keep that virus over there!” And of course I have family there as well - huge family on both sides. Thank you Miranda for being a light as Jesus taught us to be - spreading a positivity and love in these times. I got to see you in Arkansas about 2 years back I believe with friends and it was awesome. I appreciate this song and you. Thank you!!! And you being from Lindale, TX not far from me just tells more of that sweet Magnolia bloom spirit, big and beautiful and fragrant that just shines and blooms by the sunlight. 💕
